snippet.title: Mr. Run and Jump - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Run. Jump. Repeat! Originally created in 2021 as a homebrew Atari 2600 game, Mr. Run and Jump is ready to leap onto the scene with precise gameplay and an addicting challenge through the Realms of Color. Can you run and jump your way through these worlds to defeat the Void and save Leap the Dog? Mr. Run and Jump from Atari and Graphite Lab is coming soon! 

Learn more about Mr. Run and Jump: https://atari.com/products/mr-run-and-jump

Join the conversation on Discord: https://tinyurl.com/AtariDiscord

Follow Atari
Twitter: https://twitter.com/atari
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/atari
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/atari/

GRAPHITE LAB
Founded in 2009, Graphite Lab is led by owner and Studio Director Matt Raithel. The independent video game development studio produces hit titles featuring some of the world’s most visible and iconic brands. Graphite Lab specializes in bringing brands to life in fun and entertaining ways, including recent releases on PC, consoles, and mobile platforms. Graphite Lab is headquartered at 650 Maryville University Dr in St. Louis, Mo. For more information visit graphitelab.com.
